Class Notification

java.lang.Object
  org.openmobster.core.push.notification.Notification
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Notification
extends Object
implements Serializable

Encapsulates the Notification meta data to be processed by the Notifier. Notification Object is used by System components that would like to send Notifications to devices via the Notifier Service
